These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, chess, cooking
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, nigerian
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the brazilian is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Hobby      | cooking  | hiking | traveling  | chess |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian      | brazilian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
House: townhouse, tower, art-deco, palace
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the tower house is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| House   | palace | art-deco | tower   | townhouse |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, pink, blue, orange
1. the person eating corn is the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Color   | pink  | orange   | blue | chestnut    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, american, indonesian, nigerian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, family, romance
1. the mexican is on the left of the american##1
2. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
3. the mexican is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
5. the person watching romance movies is the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Nationality         | indonesian | mexican | american | nigerian |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | family     | epic    | crime       |

