.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, emerald, grey, chestnut
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Color   | emerald  | chestnut | ebony | grey |

