.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, iris, begonia
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, russian, thai, turkish
1. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the person who growsbegonia and the thai##2
4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Flower           | poppy | amaryllis | begonia | iris |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

