.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, pink, apricot, emerald
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
4. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Color   | pink     | emerald | apricot     | aquamarine   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

