.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, motorbike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
5. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
6. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Transport       | airplane       | motorbike   | snowmobile | boat |

