.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, horror, crime
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
5. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| Movie-Genre      | musical  | crime | thriller | horror |

