.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, rock, jazz, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of jazz##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | rock   | jazz | indie     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

