1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
