.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, sprite, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts, horror, drama
1. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
6. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking cola and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite  | fanta      | tea       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | drama | martial-arts | superhero |

