.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, action, martial-arts, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, tram
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | action | western | martial-arts |
| Transport     | helicopter | bike    | taxi    | tram |

