The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, salsa, rock, folk
1. the fan of rock is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | rock | folk  | techno | salsa        |

