.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, hamster, mouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, trance, soul, hip-hop
1. the owner of the bird is between the fan of trance and the owner of the goldfish##2
2. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
4. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | hamster   | mouse   | bird       | goldfish   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | trance | punk | hip-hop |

