.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, tea
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| Beverage   | juice | tea | almond-milk      | 7up        |

 